title: Zeito Dark Trendy 7/20: John Lewis, Nicki Minaj, Mark Zuckerberg, Fox News, Tenet

description:
On this edition of Zeito Dark Trendy Jack and Miles discuss the passing of Civil Rights leader, politician, and good human John Lewis, Nicki Minaj is pregnant with her first child, Mark Zuckerberg went surfing and Denny's may be trolling him introducing their 'Zuckerburger', a few Fox News personalities are being accused of sexual assault. and Tenet has been delayed indefinitely.
